 UTs. We show, through analysis, that as Q increases (with total\ntransmitted power decreased linearly with Q), the proposed low complexity\ndetector achieves a sum SE close to that achieved with optimal joint\ndemodulation at each UT. Numerical simulations confirm our analysis and also\nshow that the SE and error rate performance of the proposed OTFS based massive\nMIMO precoder and LCD detector is significantly more robust to channel induced\nDoppler spread when compared to OFDM based multi-user massive MIMO systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2020 17:29:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-25"}
