nal\nfield, modeling the full orbit of M33, will be needed to confirm its\nresemblance to observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2020 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Dec 2020 14:33:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 1 Nov 2021 22:24:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 6 Mar 2022 22:35:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-08"}
