ging complex antiferromagnetic orders at the nanoscale,\nthese results demonstrate how BiFeO$_3$ can be used as a versatile platform for\nthe design of reconfigurable nanoscale spin textures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2020 21:27:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-26"}
