y among low-income populations during the pandemic. The\nstudy illuminates an equity issue which may be of interest to policy makers and\nresearchers alike in the wake of an epidemic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Nov 2020 04:26:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 14 Feb 2021 03:03:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 12 Mar 2021 21:57:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-16"}
