 phase is estimated to\nbe1.32110-6K-1. The observed results are expected to be useful in calibration\nand performance of next generation nano-electronics and optical devices under\nextreme stress conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Nov 2020 10:26:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-26"}
